      "scd_pain_menstruation_quality_of_life_scoring": "Scoring: \"None\" = 0, \"A Few\" = 1, \"Some\" = 2, \"Many\" = 3, and \"Every\" = 4.Scores range from 0 to 28; that is, no pain burden to severe pain burden."
    }
